          "Then $AB=\\sqrt{(a\\cos t)^2+(a\\sin t)^2}=a\\sqrt{\\cos^2t+\\sin^2t}=\\boxed{a}$, independent of $t$ (with the $y$-intercept $B=(0,a\\sin t)$ found in the next method)."
